error[P002]: a standalone `{ }` block is not an expression
  --> obj.ny:2:13
   |
  2 |     let x = { }
   |             ^^^
   = label: `{ }` is a statement block, not a value
   = note: blocks run statements; they do not produce anonymous objects
   = help: use a struct literal: `MyType { field: value }`
warning[W003]: unused variable `x`
  --> obj.ny:2:9
   |
  2 |     let x = { }
   |         ^
   = label: declared here but never read
   = help: prefix with `_` if intentional: `let _x = ...`
   = help: or remove the binding if `x` is not needed
